{
  "stem": "1736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 360.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't know the seriousness of the situation, of the eventual--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we thought that they-- we didn't know what they're going to-- what's going to happen, but we knew it wasn't a good place to go.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To be confined and all this whole thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we decided to run away, and we told him so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, look, I can't do that because I have certain responsibilities.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But if your mother will give you the OK, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then there's nothing I can do about it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we made a call to my mother, and-- it was a difficult time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, regular is one-- you know, you can say regular.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to write cards to her and I used to get a few cards back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Telephones in those days were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] rare things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was expensive, we had no money, but there was contact.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, I called my mother-- I was lucky to get her-- and I explained the situation to her.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, look-- I knew I had to be careful of what I said.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said to her, I wasn't happy here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't like-- I didn't want to stay and gave all sorts of excuses why, you know, I didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she said, well, what do you want to do?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She didn't really want me to come back home, because she wasn't allowed to leave the place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, well, I want to visit Uncle Chaim.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Uncle Chaim was her brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a silence at the other side for a while, and then she said, OK.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If that's what you want to do, that's fine.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
